Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.77,0:24:17.11,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}不存在永不破晓的黑夜
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.28,0:24:21.11,difters-ed1,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}生を叫ぶ衝動 輝く
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.28,0:24:21.11,difters-ed2,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur7.5}呼喊生存的冲动 闪耀着
